# Plan 03-03 D-04: this directory holds 56 committed poster JPEGs (one per
# video in src/lib/data/videos.json). Posters are CHECKED IN to git, NOT
# gitignored — refreshing requires running `pnpm check:embeds --posters-only`
# locally and committing the diff. The build-time validatePostersPlugin in
# vite.config.ts (Plan 03-03 Task 5) verifies every video has a corresponding
# JPEG here.
#
# This .gitkeep ensures the directory survives in git even on hypothetical
# fresh clones where all *.jpg files are absent (e.g., during a future
# re-fetch via the script).
